Running.
Runnig towards it.
The target.
Sword drawn, the bounty hunter struck. 
Looking back, the ruins of his target smoldering.
 
Malice awoke, and when he tried to move, he found he also had a visitor.  Curled up next to his abdominal cavity, was a little fox, fast asleep.  While on his stay on Earth all those years ago, he learned the Japanese called them Kitsune.  Malice thought, and remembered that Camoflage was a fox, and figured this is her.  He smiled, stroked the sleeping kit, and looked over at Wolfblade.  Asleep, with Elita sleeping at her side.  He breifly wondered about the baby's mother.  He hadn't heard from her in a while.  He laid his head down, and thought about finding Nightlight after sleep.

shadowess_azogoth <shadowess_azogoth@...> wrote:
Camoflage::

She followed Elita's scent to a door. She pressed the button and the 
door opened. She sniffed around and saw Elita sleeping next to 
another femm bot. She turned her little fox head and saw another bot 
in a hammock sleeping as well. She decided, well, if you can't beat 
them, join them.  She was very careful and jumped up next to Malice. 
She curled up near his stomach and went to sleep in fox mode.
